<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA616_05_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_05_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <i class="icon_creative" lang="y"><span>창</span><span>의</span></i>
        <h2 data-head="6_orange" class="is_star" lang="y">우리 주변에서 볼 수 있는 직육면체 모양의 물건 중에서 부피를 ㎥ 단위로 나타내기에 알맞은 물건을 찾아 부피를 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box dir_col">
          <div class="table_wrap">
            <table>
              <thead class="row_color">
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">물건</th>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="서랍장" text-align="center" class="field_mid"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th class="col_color" lang="y">가로(m)</th>
                  <td lang="y">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="1.5" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th class="col_color" lang="y">세로(m)</th>
                  <td lang="y">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="0.8" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th class="col_color" lang="y">높이(m)</th>
                  <td lang="y">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <th class="col_color" lang="y">부피(㎥)</th>
                  <td lang="y">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="1.2" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
